## Operator Breakdown

- **σ (Air/Aerunik — Distinction)**: cage|prisoner — Distinguishes between identifying with constraints and recognizing oneself as the agent who holds the key.
- **ρ (Water/Sentaria — Relation)**: love|logic — Love unifies logic and emotion as a relational force connecting beings to their essential nature.
- **λ (Fire/Jvalion — Transformation)**: limitation|awakening — Displacement and limitation transform into catalysts for spiritual awakening.
- **β (Wood/Arboriel — Growth)**: displacement|belonging — The journey from feeling out of place to finding community with fellow seekers.
- **δγ (Earth/Humavita — Cycling)**: body|consciousness — Physical identification and consciousness-recognition alternate as frames of self-understanding.
- **μ (Metal/Ferrosid — Structure)**: label|essence — Movement beyond social constructs toward the essential structure of consciousness.

## Z-State
